{"tid":2232685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★美國研究發現，支肺病毒可能令人出現腦病變，康復後有機會無法自理","createTime":"2020-10-06T14:17:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T11:57:08.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9f407c38113cd2cb2ccf7deffebc8fa25a8f0ca5","tid":2232685,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:17:16.000Z","msg":"美國一項最新研究發現，<span class=\"xx-large\">病毒有可能令病人出現腦病變，患者康復後有機會無法自理</span>。傳媒也關注，美國總統特朗普日後會否面對這種情況。<br />\n<br />\n研究刊登在《臨床和轉化神經病學年鍳》，聚焦芝加哥地區新冠病毒確診入院者出現神經系統症狀的普遍性，涉及509名病人，是目前相關領域在美國最大型的研究。<br />\n<br />\n據統計，每五個人就有四個說自己有神經系統症狀，比率比中國和西班牙的同類研究為高。最多人有肌肉痛的問題，其次是頭痛，約三成一人出現腦病變，輕則有輕微意識模糊，失去短期記憶，重則陷入昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408053&amp;catCode=125&amp;topicId=552&amp;main=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408053%26catCode%3D125%26topicId%3D552%26main%3Dy&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKLYQZcr3xUkCoBtK5HAxbhw%3D&h=fe3d79a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D408053%26catCode%3D125%26topicId%3D552%26main%3Dy&h=b53e57e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=408053&amp;catCode=125&amp;topicId=552&amp;main=y</a>"},{"pid":"c32d590abf48da99defb77d95a2086eb1134d1ac","tid":2232685,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef0c817a20ce0c4f5b9f603ea8fd707bd8f1851a","tid":2232685,"uid":85168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedB